      "comment": "SECRETS WE KEEP (3) is having his first look at this course. Strong winner last time by 5 lengths at Bendigo in a Restricted WIN in the quickest time on the program (38.10). Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Ideally placed to take this out. BIG STRETCH (6) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten one length, (19.57) at Murray Bridge Straight. Leading player again. OREGON JANET (7) was an all the way winner two back but last start drifted back and wound up strongly to finish a 9 length third at Murray Bridge (40.28). Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature. CORRYONG (1) has not raced here but still warrants respect.",
